TRCP v0.1.0
---
Text Relay Communication Server, is a relay server that will bounce messages
from one client to another. TRCP can be used by any client, serving any data,
as long as it can be represented in text form.

TRCP was made to be a quick n' dirty webserver that you can start up whenever.
TRCP is universal and its up to the client to decide how data is parsed and
managed.

This  program are meant to be as small and lightweight as possible
whist allowing for quick setup and deployment. They follow a suckless
philosophy.
---

BUILDING/INSTALLING:
# first download the github repo
git clone https://github.com/x3hy/trcp
cd trcp

# start the server (blocking):
make start

# Install system-wide
sudo make install

# Test the servers connection
make conn

# To download and deploy RIGHT NOW:
git clone https://github.com/x3hy/trcp && cd trcp && make start
